KDEBUG-363067

Reference
* LUKS/Blu-ray Objective http://www.troubleshooters.com/lpm/201408/201408.htm#luksbluray_objective
* Practical malleability attack against CBC-Encrypted LUKS partitions http://www.jakoblell.com/blog/2013/12/22/practical-malleability-attack-against-cbc-encrypted-luks-partitions/

Dependence
* udftools https://sourceforge.net/projects/linux-udf/
* udisks

Usage
./make_luks_udf.sh disctype, where disctype is either blu or dvd.
Write files to /scratch/mnt/udf ...
./close_luks_udf.sh loopdevice disctype, where loopdevice is something like /dev/loop0, and disctype is either blu or dvd.
./reopen_luks_udf.sh disctype disctype is either blu or dvd.
./burn_disc disctype, where disctype is either blu or dvd.
./open_luks_disc.sh disctype, where disctype is either blu or dvd.
./close_luks_disc.sh disctype

